folder: Bowne Street & Roosevelt Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Bowne Street, north from Roosevelt Avenue. At the S. W. corner of 38th Avenue is the First of Flushing Congregational Church.
P. L. Sperr  April 8, 1927
